sub_title: International Recruitment Officer I Social Media Team Coordinator
summary:
Experienced young professional in public affairs with a demonstrated history of working in government administration and educational institutions. Skilled in office management, intercultural communication, organising events, communication strategies and project management. 

Educated in:
- Bachelor of International relations at Sofia University, Bulgaria 
- Master of Arts International Communication, the Netherlands 

I am passionate about working with diverse stakeholders, organising events and creating media content. I want to help companies develop their corporate identity and human capital.
